                <p class="text-justify">So, we've gone from one hot spot to another in the middle of summer, and who wants to carry a sweater to the tropics? In this case, a travel blanket will come in handy. I never think airline blankets are well cleaned, and I'm always concerned about germs that develop on aircraft, so I always bring my travel blanket. </p>
